CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,FAt least 59,000 people have been
OL,7,Fkilled.
OL,9,FAt least 6,000 of those died over
OL,10,Fthree days in October, when the RSF
OL,11,Frampaged through the Darfur outpost of
OL,12,Fel-Fasher, according to the UN, with
OL,13,FUN-backed experts concluding the
OL,14,Foffensive bore "the defining
OL,15,Fcharacteristics of genocide".
OL,17,FIn response to the anniversary, the UK
OL,18,FForeign Office announced it would
OL,19,Fpledge #146 to support humanitarian
OL,20,Fefforts in the region.
OL,26,@vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
