PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,F#15m of the funding will be carved out
OL,7,Fto fund emergency responders to reach
OL,8,Fover 1.8 million people in need.
OL,10,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,11,F"Sudan's civilians are already doing
OL,12,Ftheir part. Their courage is inspiring.
OL,14,F"That is why we are protecting the
OL,15,FUK's humanitarian support to Sudan and
OL,16,Fdoubling our funding to these local
OL,17,Fresponders, helping them to reach
OL,18,Fnearly 2 million people."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
