CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,FThe World Food Programme estimates
OL,7,Fmore than 19 million people face acute
OL,8,Fhunger.
OL,10,FAnd now fuel prices in Sudan have
OL,11,Fincreased by over 24% because of the
OL,12,FIran war and its effects on shipping,
OL,13,Fdriving up food prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
