PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,F"A plea from me: Please don't call
OL,7,Fthis the forgotten crisis. I'm
OL,8,Freferring to this as an abandoned
OL,9,Fcrisis," the top UN official in Sudan,
OL,10,FDenise Brown, said Monday, criticising
OL,11,Fthe international community for
OL,12,Ffailing to focus on ending the
OL,13,Ffighting.
OL,15,FThe war exploded from a power struggle
OL,16,Fthat emerged following Sudan's
OL,17,Ftransition to democracy after an
OL,18,Fuprising forced the military ouster of
OL,19,Flongtime dictator Omar al-Bashir in
OL,20,FApril 2019.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
