OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,FThree years of fighting have seen
OL,7,Fwidespread atrocities, including mass
OL,8,Fkillings and rampant sexual violence,
OL,9,Fincluding gang rapes.
OL,11,FHospitals, ambulances and medical
OL,12,Fworkers in Sudan have been attacked,
OL,13,Fwith over 2,000 people killed, the WHO
OL,14,Fhas said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776255070
OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,FThe International Criminal Court has
OL,7,Fsaid it was investigating potential
OL,8,Fwar crimes and crimes against
OL,9,Fhumanity, particularly in Darfur, a
OL,10,Fregion that two decades ago became
OL,11,Fsynonymous with genocide and war
OL,12,Fcrimes.
OL,14,FMost of the latest atrocities have
OL,15,Fbeen blamed on the RSF and their
OL,16,FJanjaweed allies, Arab militias that
OL,17,Fwere notorious for atrocities in the
OL,18,Fearly 2000s against people identifying
OL,19,Fas East or Central African in Darfur.
OL,20,FThe RSF grew out of the Janjaweed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
