OL,3,C'Abandoned': Aid organisations sound
OL,4,Calarm as Sudan war enters fourth year
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe military's seizure of Khartoum and
OL,12,Fother urban areas in central Sudan in
OL,13,Fearly 2025 did allow the return of
OL,14,Fabout 4 million people to their homes,
OL,15,Fthe UN migration agency said in March.
OL,16,FBut they struggle with damaged
OL,17,Finfrastructure and other challenges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
